{"tid":1434300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東方：兩警執勤甩漏　遺失通訊器及警棍","createTime":"2019-08-08T17:30:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T03:49:30.000Z","uid":91914,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fd0a930d93330a86d857028a329121786d26b45f","tid":1434300,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:30:33.000Z","msg":"仲狙擊緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本周一（5日），一名隸屬警察機動部隊的警務人員，於凌晨2時許，在黃大仙一帶執行職務時，大意遺失一部警察通訊器。此外，一名隸屬鐵路警區的警務人員，同日上午9時許，在港鐵荔景站執行職務時同樣大意，遺失一支伸縮警棍。 <br />\n<br />\n警方得悉器材遺失後，隨即展開調查，並於現場一帶搜尋，惟未有發現。案件列作「遺失政府財物」，由有關人員所屬單位跟進調查。有關警察通訊器亦隨即被終止服務及已失效。警方呼籲市民如拾獲有關物品，應立即交到就近的警署。警方重申，警隊就裝備的保管及使用有嚴格的規定。警方會繼續就有關事件作出跟進。 <br />\n<br />\n本月4日，反對《逃犯條例》修例人士分別在將軍澳及西區舉行集會遊行，結果演變成多區遊擊戰，入夜後有示威者包圍黃大仙警察宿舍，並於龍翔道設置路障，至翌日凌晨時分，防暴警施放多枚催淚彈驅散人群。本月5日早上，反修例人士發起「三罷」行動，亦有人發起港鐵不合作運動，港鐵服務一度受影響，至同日下午約1時始陸續回復正常"},{"pid":"7a6c9df2f649635ac6f00fc44a9fbd9c57be9213","tid":1434300,"uid":161037,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:35:06.000Z","msg":"得罪咗方丈仲想走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"925172a314903487108fcbdd709c2ed7dbc95bbf","tid":1434300,"uid":108606,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:36:02.000Z","msg":"雖遠必誅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f084163d501421cf0502afa27c360273ec312139","tid":1434300,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:44:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d47ffb068afecee24026af5c58e0e40820db7f99","tid":1434300,"uid":112551,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:15:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f53bcedf354f569fdcb4ee54d54108ebcff55f8d","tid":1434300,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:42:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b23aac0881a8e0f5472034cc01a05a4a06ab73","tid":1434300,"uid":255963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:47:39.000Z","msg":"因管理不善而排名節節下降 . .."},{"pid":"ab7637fb6c12e7ebafe569b8c56f2a4808862877","tid":1434300,"uid":204309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:48:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黑警唔死都一身散<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c859c28953004cb07a106b84270a8d53afbeef7e","tid":1434300,"uid":260036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:49:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}